            <title>[FLINK-24468] NPE when notifyNewBufferSize</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-24468</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In my opinion, we have two problem there:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The exception itself(see below)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Ignoring the exception and stopping rescheduling of the calculation of the buffer size.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Of course, we need to fix this NPE and we need to think what we want to do if the buffer debloat fails with error.&lt;/p&gt;

